OL,3,CFarmer fined #50,000 for faking
OL,4,Csalmonella test results
OL,6,FA farmer has been ordered to pay more
OL,7,Fthan #50,000 for failing to test
OL,8,Fchickens and eggs for salmonella
OL,9,Fbefore they went into the food chain.
OL,11,FStuart Perkins, 38, from Radstock in
OL,12,FSomerset, was also found to have
OL,13,Fpresented birds for slaughter with
OL,14,Feither fake documents or with
OL,15,Fdocumentation which did not relate to
OL,16,Fthose particular birds.
OL,18,FAt Bath Magistrates Court he admitted
OL,19,Ffailing to carry out the legally
OL,20,Frequired testing for two years.
