OL,3,CFarmer fined #50,000 for faking
OL,4,Csalmonella test results
OL,6,FBy law, farms producing eggs are
OL,7,Frequired to conduct salmonella tests
OL,8,Fin their poultry sheds every 15 weeks
OL,9,Fduring the laying period.
OL,11,FWhen an inspector visited his farm
OL,12,FPerkins produced 16 reports dated back
OL,13,Fto August 2021, 13 of which had been
OL,14,Ffalsified.
