OL,3,CFarmer fined #50,000 for faking
OL,4,Csalmonella test results
OL,6,FFakir Mohamed Osman, from the South
OL,7,FWest Trading Standards Service said:
OL,8,F"We take breaches of this kind very
OL,9,Fseriously. The prevention of
OL,10,Fsalmonella programme is there for a
OL,11,Freason, to safeguard the public.
OL,12,FProducers suspected of not carrying
OL,13,Fout the required testing will be
OL,14,Finvestigated.
OL,16,F"The defendant's actions presented a
OL,17,Freal risk to public health, and I am
OL,18,Fpleased that, thanks to our
OL,19,Fcollaborative efforts with the Food
OL,20,FStandards Agency, we were able to take
OL,21,Faction".
