OL,3,CFarmer fined #50,000 for faking
OL,4,Csalmonella test results
OL,6,FPerkins and his company, SG Perkins
OL,7,FLimited was ordered to pay a total of
OL,8,F#50,830.75.
OL,10,FAndrew Quinn, from the Food Standards
OL,11,FAgency's National Food Crime Unit
OL,12,Fsaid: "We welcome this substantial
OL,13,Ffine as it shows the serious nature of
OL,14,Ffaking documents and jeopardising food
OL,15,Fsafety.
OL,17,F"This should act as a deterrent to
OL,18,Fanyone else considering taking
OL,19,Fdangerous shortcuts and breaching food
OL,20,Fsafety and hygiene law."
